{"tid":274684,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"暗榮係PS4度出Dissidia Final Fantasy NT","createTime":"2017-06-07T13:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T03:34:58.000Z","uid":14812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30332857b4f5abcf92c861d4472a260a939b9714","tid":274684,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5WjoFD5Xdqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5WjoFD5Xdqk&d=Lwq37QuzZXg%2B2cZCUkfRWAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d7a73168\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5WjoFD5Xdqk</a><br />\n<br />\n　　《Dissidia Final Fantasy》是 KOEI TECMO Games Team NINJA 開發、以《Final Fantasy》系列為題材的大型電玩對戰動作遊戲。遊戲中玩家可以選擇自己喜歡的角色自由組隊、設定能發動威力強大之超必殺技的「召喚獸」，在熟悉的歷代場景對戰舞台中，展開 3 對 3 的激烈對戰。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n　　根據 Amazon 透露的商品介紹資訊，本次預定推出的 PS4 版《Dissidia Final Fantasy NT》將收錄超過 20 名可用角色，超過 10 個經典對戰場地，多種傳奇召喚獸，以及大量可供裝備的武器與莫古利。玩家可以透過戰鬥來取得經驗值與金錢，升級強化 EX 技能、武器與造型，打造屬於自己的 FF 冠軍戰士，體驗由野島一成（代表作：《Final Fantasy VII》等）編劇的全新 FF 故事。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n　　由於大型電玩版當初就是以 PS4 主機為基礎的系統來開發，因此上市營運後各方就預期後續會在 PS4 上推出家用版。如今 Amazon 率先透露了家用版的消息，後續 SQUARE ENIX 也在今日舉辦的直播節目「Dissidia Final Fantasy 官方直播#9.5＋？」中確認 PS4 版將於 2018 年初推出。在下週登場的美國 E3 展中預料會有更進一步的展出或試玩，有興趣的玩家不妨多多留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/4/147954.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F4%2F147954.html&d=Lwq37QuzZXg%2B2cZCUkfRWAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=411626ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/4/147954.html</a>"},{"pid":"fc073272b463b175dfdf9782e4c6f8225bdc7baf","tid":274684,"uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"終於出家用版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3690ec16a65c43907ac78cd80f0cab593d211a1a","tid":274684,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"好正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c33b0f8ebd627b4b6fe2b555acef9a8fd7fc293","tid":274684,"uid":119402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004bdb304dc41eb6aacd7771bfad7d0ea105913f","tid":274684,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 終於出<br />\n之前成日睇日本仔d街機片已經好想玩呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed78836b3dcdd3d6fa309471b787cf6370307944","tid":274684,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"好鐘意dissidia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專登去日本玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec5b96df85f40bf91d18ef1084bbc7da1c6d47f","tid":274684,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:42:23.000Z","msg":"黎緊兩年又有gvs又有呢隻 好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757d4c5846717895eeaa47c61d93321997bce8d2","tid":2